{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fb1057763b","title":"陈少山、乔雪村、赵凯对雅安地区治病情况向省委的报告","origin":"四川省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e15bf8459c","index":0,"year":1960,"month":4,"day":11,"articleId":"fb1057763b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"36962fdb53","type":"title","text":"陈少山、乔雪村、赵凯对雅安地区治病情况向省委的报告","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b"},{"id":"073543c5ba","type":"appellation","text":"中共四川省委生活福利委员会办公××","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b"},{"id":"c461661576","type":"appellation","text":"收文第33号","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b"},{"id":"1d30893a11","type":"appellation","text":"4月14日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b"},{"id":"c7cbbad6e6","type":"appellation","text":"中共四川省委办公厅收文第7492号","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b"},{"id":"b297808a77","type":"appellation","text":"××年6月12日(原件年份缺失，应为1960或1961年)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b"},{"id":"6cce66a4f1","type":"appellation","text":"省委：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b"},{"id":"6a0a5a2a73","type":"paragraph","text":"我们最近集合各组组长在雅安学习文件，检查工作三天，对雅安区群众生活、农业生产、毛猪等三个方面整理出三个材料，送上请审阅指示。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b"},{"id":"9fa6922070","type":"paragraph","text":"李政委、刘部长、张付部长昨天来雅安指示工作，并已曾派张敏、慕世友二同志参加工作（张到天全、慕到宝兴），原驻县工作的四个组，除荣经、名山二组不动外，其余汉源组调宝兴。芦山一组调天全，这四个县都是病人较多的地区。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b"},{"id":"5ee32daf47","type":"paragraph","text":"关于治病，四月八日止，全区总病人数为48,643人，已集中治疗40,001人。4月1日以来，每日死亡一百二、三十人左右。以荣经、名山、天全三县较多，治病措施地委已根据省委指示安排，各县都加强了领导。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b"},{"id":"30ad666209","type":"paragraph","text":"抄送：省委农工部、雅安地委。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b"},{"id":"6e2d8930d6","type":"paragraph","text":" 陈少山乔雪村赵  凯四月十一日","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b"}],"page":{"id":"fef6a478d7","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fb1057763b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}